    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "余七",
        "余六",
        "沈球"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四下手、八头领、余六、余七同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "余七 （同点绛唇） 胆量包天，熊腰虎面，称好汉，霸占浮山，绿林美名传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余六",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "霸占浮山有数秋，杀人放火俺为头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余七",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虽然不是森落殿，亚赛朝廷五凤楼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余六、余七",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾，"
        },
        {
          "character": "余六",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "捉鱼鹞子余六。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余七",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "混海蛟龙余七。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余六",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "弟兄二人，镇守浮山，倒也逍遥自在，也曾命喽啰，随同大头目沈球，下山探\n寻买卖，怎么还不见到来？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（沈球上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "沈球",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忙将山下事，报于寨主知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "沈球",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见二位寨主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余六",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "沈球回来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "沈球",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余六",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "山下可有什么生意买卖？"
        },
        {
          "character": "沈球",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "生意买卖倒没有，倒打听一桩新闻来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余六",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么新闻？"
        },
        {
          "character": "沈球",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人言施不全奉命出朝，已经来在此处下马啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余六",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既是赃官到此，我等倒要留心准备。就命你，带领四十名喽啰，在山口把守，\n须要小心。不得违误。"
        },
        {
          "character": "沈球",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（沈球下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "余六",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔等小心把守山寨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
