    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "贺天保"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贺天保上，趟马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺天保",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "乔装改扮出衙门，\n要到浮山走一程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺天保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，赛专诸贺天保。是俺私自出衙，要探浮山路径，就此前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺天保",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "来在山口用目看，\n号令人头为哪般？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贺天保",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，山口之上，为何有一鲜血淋漓的人头在此号令？哦喝是了，想是我黄贤弟，\n私自前来探山，被那贼拿住杀死，号令在此。我若不替他报仇，还等何时？\n呔！贼人休得逞强，俺贺天保来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贺天保入山，下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 5,
          "唱": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 1.0,
        "dominant_style_family": "西皮",
        "musical_styles": [
          "西皮摇板"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 7,
      "label": "第七场",
      "characters_present": [
        "管宁"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（管宁上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "管宁",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "心中只把贼人恨，\n特地前来探贼人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "管宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，管宁，闻听大人，要灭那浮山贼寇，传下令来：只准明察，不准暗探。众\n家英雄，在衙前商议，准备明日，同探山寨。是俺私自出衙，暗为探访，倘若\n探的真情，岂不是大大一功也？"
        },
        {
          "character": "管宁",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "急急忙忙往前闯，"
        },
        {
          "character": "管宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "管宁",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "高挂人头为哪桩？"
        },
        {
          "character": "管宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "山口之上，挂一人头号令，不知何人之头？待俺用袖剑将他射下。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（管宁射人头落地。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "管宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，我当是谁？原来是卢志义的人头。想是他前来探山，被贼人杀死，待俺\n闯进山去，看个明白，再作道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（管宁入山，下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
